# QR Code Component

This project is a simple **QR Code component** built using only HTML and CSS.  
The component displays a **QR code** along with a title and description, and it can be used as part of any webpage or learning project.

---

## 📦 Project Contents

- `index.html` – Contains the basic structure of the component.
- `style.css` – Contains the styling for the component.
- `qrcode.png` – The QR code image used in the project.

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- Flexbox
- Box-shadow and Border-radius
- Responsive design

---

## 💡 Component Features

- Clean and organized design with a colored background and box shadow.
- Elements (image, title, text) are centered.
- Easily customizable in terms of colors, fonts, and image size.
- Can be reused in any project as a standalone **QR Code component**.

---

## 📐 How to Use

1. Copy the project files (`index.html`, `style.css`, `qrcode.png`) into your project.
2. Open `index.html` in a browser to preview the component.
3. Modify the text and image as needed.

---

## 🌐 Preview

You can preview the component directly by opening `index.html` in any modern browser.

---

This project was designed as part of hands-on HTML and CSS learning and can be used as a **standalone component** in any web project.
